summary: This is really just a test but I plan to expand it in time. The goal will be to edit the placement of objects in the game world. I feel that the placement of many world objects are sloppy and sometimes this creates massive clipping between the objects.
descriptionHtml:
This is really just a test but I plan to expand it in time. The goal will be to edit the placement of objects in the game world. I feel that the placement of many world objects are sloppy and sometimes this creates massive clipping between the objects.

Suggestions for world/cell edits are welcome.

Put the .esp before any lighting/similar mods.

v0.1 Temple of Dibella is done
author: silverdragon5
